
Get from
http://www.cs.sandia.gov/Zoltan/

export PREFIX=wherever
export FC=ftn
export CC=cc
export CXX=CC

mkdir build
cd build
 ../configure \
 --prefix=$PREFIX \
 --enable-mpi --with-mpi-compilers \
 --enable-f90interface 

Zoltan can use parametis.  The above is without parametis,
to be used with FUN3D, which has its own parametis interface.

make everything
make install



